RT and <a href="/hashtag/VoteLabour?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>VoteLabour</b></a> <a href="https://t.co/kLKOybdydu" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/kLKOybdydu</a></p>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Good evening in Windsor Drive <a href="/hashtag/Yate?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>Yate</b></a> <a href="/hashtag/LabourDoorstep?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>LabourDoorstep</b></a> - met  Labour voters and some undecided who will check out manifesto.</p>

<p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="3">Jeremy Corbyn added,</p>

  if(window.ttft){
    window.ttft.recordMilestone('page', document.getElementById('swift-page-name').getAttribute('content'));
    window.ttft.recordMilestone('section', document.getElementById('swift-section-name').getAttribute('content'));
    window.ttft.recordMilestone('client_record_time', window.ttft.now());
  }
